{"tid":2036161,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"★內地有錢人增購海外物業　點解香港冇份？","createTime":"2020-05-26T09:53:40.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-26T10:01:15.000Z","uid":19454,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"0bc4389a2be48c36734a0af922073fde36c07c6b","tid":2036161,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-26T09:53:40.000Z","msg":"由於香港靠近中國內地，而且市場限制較少，因此曾經是最受歡迎的目的地。但是，由於社會動盪，許多有錢的內地人轉向新加坡，作為替代方案，這並不受高稅率的影響。第一季度，香港豪宅價格下跌了4.5%，是新加坡跌幅的兩倍。<br />\nERA的Foo表示，由於新加坡的穩定，內地買家認為新加坡的房地產市場是避風港。與香港相比，新加坡是一個更加規範的市場<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/finance/20200526/bkn-20200526115536432-0526_00842_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Ffinance%2F20200526%2Fbkn-20200526115536432-0526_00842_001.html&d=SVgHbq7l0Cva0E6q1evMAwPtErjweJPees2C482IDEo%3D&h=c87ba89c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/finance/20200526/bkn-20200526115536432-0526_00842_001.html</a>"},{"pid":"7ef81bb9777a003ddf9ae73bbfcd60b34a3e8d50","tid":2036161,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-26T09:53:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"82b9b25450376205e7e91ea573a42dae3748a61f","tid":2036161,"uid":213877,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-26T10:01:15.000Z","msg":"有你都唔知啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}